name: CW_AGE_JUL2025_YR
title: Age of Cow
description: Age (in years) of cow at the start of the trial, calculated from start date of trial period minus cow birthdate

name: CW_GENO_ID
title: Cow Genotype ID
description: The genotype identification number of the cows

name: CW_PGDT
title: Cow PregTest Date
description: Date cow is Preg-Checked, and often the same date as the calf is weaned (YYYY-MM-DD)

name: CW_PGPREG
title: Pregnancy Status
description: Pregnancy diagnosis of cow at preg-check (P=Pregnant;O=Open;.=missing data)

name: CW_PGWT_KG
title: Cow PregTest Weight
description: Cow weight at preg check in kg, collected from raw weight files

name: CW_Pred_PGWT_KG
title: Cow predicted Pregnancy Weight
description: Cow predicted Pregnancy Weight in kg

name: CW_REMARKS
title: General remarks about cow
description: Will include general remarks about the cow before and after prebreed, ie. Treatments, notes regarding fostering, etc.

name: CW_TAG
title: Visual Cow Tag
description: Corresponds to the visual cow ID tag

name: CW_YR_LETTER
title: Year Letter of Cow
description: Letter that reflects the year animal was born in

name: RANCH
title: Ranch name
description: The ranch where the animal belong (Kinsella or Mattheis)

name: RFI_gEPD
title: Cow genomic estimated Expected Progeny Difference
description: Cow genomic estimated Expected Progeny Difference
